# M5 P07 — Touch-driven CTF flag pickup on Crossfire.
#
# Verifies that ctf_step's per-tick touch detection actually fires at
# runtime (not just via the flag_carry debug directive). The player
# (RED) spawns just west of the BLUE flag, walks RIGHT a few px into
# it, and the flag transitions to CARRIED.
#
# Crossfire BLUE flag: x = 4160, y = 974 (chest-height above platform).

window 1280 720
out build/shots/m5_ctf_pickup
seed 1 2

map crossfire
mode ctf

# Spawn ~80 px west of the BLUE flag so we walk RIGHT into it.
spawn_at 4080 950

contact_sheet ctf_pickup cols 4 cell 320 180

at 1   shot t1_pre_walk
at 30  shot t30_settled

# Walk RIGHT for ~30 ticks (~140 px). Pickup should fire when chest x
# crosses into 36 px of flag x = 4160 (i.e. when chest_x >= 4124).
at 35 press right
at 90 release right

# Pickup expected around tick 50–60. Capture a frame after.
at 70 shot t70_after_pickup
at 100 shot t100_holding_blue

at 120 end
